songs.title: I Go In
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Tell me, Mr. Connor
(Tell you what, Charlie?)
Just tell me
(I don't know what you're talking about bro)
Um...

[Verse 1]
Tell me
Who went and threw the best party last night
That was me, me, me, me, me, me
(You)
I had women on the couch
And on top of the roof
And all over the TV screen
And everybody was like:
"Oh my god
Charlie Puth
You sure know how to throw a party, dude"
I'm the coolest motherfucker
You can hear it in the song
And I don't even need to kid
Octo-Mom

[Pre-Chorus]
Every single day
Cooking like Rachel Ray
(Swag!)
I'm doin my thing
Single ladies, Beyonce
I came to win
Where have you been?
Bitch when I go out, out, out, out
I go in

[Chorus]
Yeah, get on the floor
Get up, get up
Give me some more
Tonight, tonight, tonight, tonight
I'm going in tonight
Shawty over there, looking like a ten
I ain't gonna leave till 6 am
Tonight, tonight, tonight, tonight
I'm going in tonight

[Verse 2]
You can call me Oliver Twist cause I always want some more
(More porridge)
And if you ain't never gonna party
Get your ass up out the door
(Get out)
All you imitators why you gotta be so whack? (Whack)
I'm so sweet (sweet)
Hostess snack (Twinkie)
I'm a ghost buster, all you do is call
I'm so humurous, Luciel Ball!

[Pre-Chorus]
Every single day

(Swag!)
I'm doin my thing

I came to win
Where have you been?
Bitch when I go out, out, out, out
I go in

Tonight, tonight, tonight, tonight
I'm going in tonight
Shawty over there, looking like a ten
I ain't gonna leave till 6 am
Tonight, tonight, tonight, tonight
I'm going in tonight

Yo, I'm the migida-migida-migida-migida Mac Daddy (ooh)
I'm the migida-migida-migida-migida Mac (ah)
They call me the migida-migida-migida-migida Mac Daddy (ooh)
I'm the migida-migida-migida-migida Mac (ah)
You're the migida-migida-migida-migida Mac Daddy
I'm the migida-migida-migida-migida Mac
I'm the Mac Daddy
I'm the migida-migida-migida-migida Mac
(Swag!)

I came to win
Where have you been?
Bitch when I go out, out, out, out

Give me some more
